rows.name:
One of my friends gave me an
awesome tip the other day.

rows.label: tlk41100121_03_msg0002
rows.name:
So, you know how there's a type of
rock shaped all funny like? Called
Dilemma Rock?

rows.label: tlk41100121_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Yeah, my friend said you can pick 'em
up by the dozen in rocky places like
Dawnview Grotto and Twin Trunks Hill.
